data.description: Don't Miss your opportunity to own 35 acres of this Secluded acreage oasis on the Edge of Tiger Lake. Here is your chance to own serenity and peace along SR60. Fish, Hunt, Camp and Cattle your way to a blissful lifestyle and make lasting memories. Build your own country estate on the best site on the property already elevated to overlook the most scenic views. Build your dream home with easy access to SR60 that connects to all the nearby amenities the surrounding areas have to offer. Embark on the journey of freedom and true seclusion. This paradise is a hidden Gem with surprises all around. 70 Acres total on the parcel can be split 35 acres each or purchased together.
